<text>Trajectory

&lt; Previous | Index | Next &gt;

The trajectory command shows or hides the trajectories of the centers of mass of the selected objects. (To see how to show and hide the trajectory of the center of mass of an object without using scripts, see this section.)

Syntax:

trajectory ON/OFF
traj ON/OFF

The second is an abbreviation of the first.

 
Note: If the recorder is disabled, turning on the trajectory has no effect --- because the trajectories are not recorded.
 

  
 
[This is an embedded simulator.]
